{
  "id": "69c2a2fd9cd319df1a45805a",
  "title": "ホクホクの食べ物",
  "created": 1774363390,
  "updated": 1774403435,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd9cd319df1a45805a",
      "text": "ホクホクの食べ物",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363390
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab235c",
      "text": " [かぼちゃ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774390524
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab235d",
      "text": " [さつまいも]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774390527
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab235e",
      "text": " [じゃがいも]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774390530
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab235f",
      "text": " [そら豆]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774390533
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a38c0000000000937f88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363532,
      "updated": 1774363532
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a38d0000000000937f89",
      "text": " 基本的に野菜なのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774363533,
      "updated": 1774390565
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a3190000000000937f84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363418,
      "updated": 1774363418
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2360",
      "text": " [ホクホク性]は食感、温度、味にまたがる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2361",
      "text": " 無味でもホクホクすることがあるかもしれない",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2362",
      "text": " \tおでんに入っている厚く切った大根をイメージ[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2363",
      "text": " \t\t無味ではないが大根は薄味、おでんの出汁がメインかなと",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2364",
      "text": " \t世の中には染みてない大根のほうがすきという人がいるようだ(脱線）[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363458
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a37c0000000000937f87",
      "text": " \t 植物感？というか",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363516,
      "updated": 1774363529
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2365",
      "text": " 熱いそら豆は食感がホクホクとはあまり思わないないが、味が口に広がるとホクホクと感じる",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2366",
      "text": "  なんかわかる[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2367",
      "text": "   カリフラワーなんかもちょっとホクホクの感じがある",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774363397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c2a2fd0000000000ab2368",
      "text": " [にんにく]もホクホク[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1774363390,
      "updated": 1774403435
    },
    {
      "id": "69c33f5f00000000002ac541",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1774403424,
      "updated": 1774403424
    }
  ]
}